/artists/Zulu">Zulu</a> ，Zulu， <a href="/artists/Gel">Gel</a> ， <a href="/artists/IDLES">Idles</a> ， <a href="/artists/Touche-Amore">Touche Amore</a>等人的封面和混音。 Lyxzén和Sandström的班轮笔记以及《致敬》专辑中的乐队的书面贡献还将包括在专辑的遗产中提供新的背景和见解。限量版的“朋克形状来临”将仅由全球2000册组成，可以<a href="https://refusedband.ffm.to/theshapeofpunktocome" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订</a>。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到LP时，乐队分享了：“无论记录对其他所有人意味着什么，这都代表着我们年轻和恶魔般的护理时生活中的一个了不起的时光，我们正在冒险，想证明我们勇敢，比我们想庆祝这一点的其他任何事情都要多：疯狂，野性的组合，纯粹的创造力。</p><p> “因此，我们要求一群我们喜欢和尊重的艺术家实际上是用歌曲自由，重新安排或完全解构材料，以使引擎本质上拆开，并且对此并不珍贵。他们不是，对我们来说，这是对我们记录的唯一致敬：我们的英雄，年轻的枪支以及老朋友和同伴，通过发现其中的新可能性和新含义来称赞我们的音乐。这些乐队都是将军的鱼子酱，我们很荣幸他们花了一些时间参与其中。谢谢大家。” </p><figure id="attachment_3792396" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792396" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792396" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused-The-Shape-Of-Whats-To-Come-Obliterated-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="拒绝了“即将被淘汰的形状”专辑插图。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused-The-Shape-Of-Whats-To-Come-Obliterated-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused-The-Shape-Of-Whats-To-Come-Obliterated-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused-The-Shape-Of-Whats-To-Come-Obliterated-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused-The-Shape-Of-Whats-To-Come-Obliterated-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused-The-Shape-Of-Whats-To-Come-Obliterated-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused-The-Shape-Of-Whats-To-Come-Obliterated-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused-The-Shape-Of-Whats-To-Come-Obliterated-album-artwork.-Credit-P